name: Tocen
additional_notices: No active trades are found for this coin. Please submit a ticket at %{link} if you think this is an error.

description.en:
What is the project about?
Tocen is an one-stop, aggregated platform for Gamefi – Defi – NFTfi. We are building simplified, easy to use dApps & addictive games on Sui Network with a vision of onboarding millions of newcomers to Web3.

What makes your project unique?
Tocen is an all-in-one platform, whose the mission is to be easy-to-use for billions users.

History of your project.
Tocen had run IDO & INO on Sui Network.
Funds from IDO: 705,000 $SUI

What’s next for your project?
Tocen team planned to finalize the Game Hub, Dex Aggregator on Q2 & we are looking forwards to CEX listing.

What can your token be used for?
$TOCE is the core governance token of Tocen launchpad and other non-launchpad products. The token use cases are bootstrapping DAO rights, elevating the benefits of Master Key NFTs, participating in exclusive token/NFT sales, earning with staking rewards and more.

Tocen is an one-stop, aggregated platform for Gamefi – Defi – NFTfi. We are building simplified, easy to use dApps & addictive games on Sui Network with a vision of onboarding millions of newcomers to Web3.

What makes your project unique?
Tocen is an all-in-one platform, whose the mission is to be easy-to-use for billions users.

History of your project.
Tocen had run IDO & INO on Sui Network.
Funds from IDO: 705,000 $SUI

What’s next for your project?
Tocen team planned to finalize the Game Hub, Dex Aggregator on Q2 & we are looking forwards to CEX listing.

What can your token be used for?
$TOCE is the core governance token of Tocen launchpad and other non-launchpad products. The token use cases are bootstrapping DAO rights, elevating the benefits of Master Key NFTs, participating in exclusive token/NFT sales, earning with staking rewards and more.
